<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10939</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空到了普陀山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有个孩子正在花园里坐禅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“观音菩萨在哪里？”悟空问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27143</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她在做篮子。”孩子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抬头看了悟空一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很高兴再见到你，悟空。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空有点儿疑惑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么知道我的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不认识我了吗？”孩子问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空盯着孩子看了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48879</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他大吃一惊。“你是红孩儿！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48880</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你现在看上去像个神仙了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”红孩儿说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不再是个妖怪了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我得谢谢你。是你让我见到了观音菩萨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她教了我很多。现在我很快乐。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不客气。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你和我有很多相似的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们曾做过坏事，惹了很多麻烦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，我们又都向佛了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨走了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她手里提着一个篮子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，悟空。”观音菩萨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你今天会来这里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以我一早上都在做这个篮子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空很疑惑。“这篮子不错，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是它有什么用呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个篮子是有法力的。”观音菩萨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要用它去捉妖怪。我们走吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和观音菩萨一起来到了河边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨用一根绳子把篮子放入了河里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她念了句咒语，等了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她又把篮子从河里拉了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看了下篮子里面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有条小金鱼正在篮子里跳跃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑。“观音菩萨，我觉得你得再试一次。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这可不是那妖怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我的金鱼。”观音菩萨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它之前一直生活在我的莲花池里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莲花池在我教导弟子的花园旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171010</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这条金鱼一直听我讲经。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171011</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很多年后，它成了精。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几天前，它逃到了凡间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我一直在想它去了哪里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“几天前。”悟空重复道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就是说他在凡间已经几年了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对！”观音菩萨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“唐僧现在安全了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你去救他，继续你们的西天取经之路吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跳到河里，向宫殿游去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，那条金鱼已经不在了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它的法术也消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空用金箍棒砸碎了巨石，走了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父，我来了！”悟空大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把唐僧从石箱里救了出来，带着他回到了河面上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，所有村民都听说悟空救了老陈的儿子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当悟空他们回到村子里的时候，村民们都欢呼了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请留在我们的村子里吧。”一个男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊。”一个老妇人也说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别急着走。你们想在这里留多久都可以。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你们。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们只能再住一晚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>明天一早，我们就必须得走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们还有很远的路要走。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，村民们为他们举行了盛宴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等到大家都睡觉的时候，已经是深夜了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一早，唐僧他们就被伐木的声音吵醒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生了什么事情？”唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们走到了河边，看到了村民们正在忙碌的景象。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个男人正在伐树。其他人在搬运工具。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在为你们造船呢！”一个男人微笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你们。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一行人在河边坐下来等着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，河里发出一阵巨响，河水溅到了河岸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都害怕地看着河里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个巨大的黑影从波浪中升了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>